{"tid":1973291,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"小明被女手足的一句話欺騙了","createTime":"2020-04-15T06:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T13:49:18.000Z","uid":199804,"like":56,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f01cdd5d20e3802691eaeb7f93a07c210ffbb167","tid":1973291,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"小明係一個連登仔。<br />\n有一日，連登開始有一堆自稱女手足嘅會員講<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只嫁前線巴，</strong></span><br />\n小明見到，就諗住終於有機會擺脫因為樣衰而溝唔到女嘅現狀，開始去遊行示威打狗，最後仲上埋前線<br />\n點知比狗打，放火，甚至入去坐左幾碌，出到黎都冇女埋身。於是小明決定揾佢中學時暗戀左好耐嘅女神，想同佢表白，因為佢記得女神喺ig story share過只嫁前線巴嘅post。小明諗住今次實冇死，自己乜都做齊曬，絕對係前線手足嘅典範。於是小明pm女神ig,<br />\n&ldquo;我係前線巴，而你又只嫁前線巴，咁你可否同我一齊？&rdquo;<br />\n女神回覆：&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死毒撚咪ff la!</span></span>你係咪痴線㗎,我男朋友是前線，我只嫁給他，關你撚事？！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明失望了，他照鏡看看自己<br />\n其實上了前線，他沒有比較英俊，也沒有比較強壯<br />\n他現在明白了<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只嫁前線巴</span>不是指上前線她就嫁給你<br />\n只是，她的伴侶本身已經是前線巴。。。"},{"pid":"805c80140038473d5b314cd8372e0a74a4f86076","tid":1973291,"uid":68084,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"f01cdd5d20e3802691eaeb7f93a07c210ffbb167","tid":1973291,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"小明係一個連登仔。<br />\n有一日，連登開始有一堆自稱女手足嘅會員講<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只嫁前線巴，</strong></span><br />\n小明見到，就諗住終於有機會擺脫因為樣衰而溝唔到女嘅現狀，開始去遊行示威打狗，最後仲上埋前線<br />\n點知比狗打，放火，甚至入去坐左幾碌，出到黎都冇女埋身。於是小明決定揾佢中學時暗戀左好耐嘅女神，想同佢表白，因為佢記得女神喺ig story share過只嫁前線巴嘅post。小明諗住今次實冇死，自己乜都做齊曬，絕對係前線手足嘅典範。於是小明pm女神ig,<br />\n&ldquo;我係前線巴，而你又只嫁前線巴，咁你可否同我一齊？&rdquo;<br />\n女神回覆：&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死毒撚咪ff la!</span></span>你係咪痴線㗎,我男朋友是前線，我只嫁給他，關你撚事？！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小明失望了，他照鏡看看自己<br />\n其實上了前線，他沒有比較英俊，也沒有比較強壯<br />\n他現在明白了<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只嫁前線巴</span>不是指上前線她就嫁給你<br />\n只是，她的伴侶本身已經是前線巴。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好波<br />\n<br />\n等睇一堆只嫁<br />\n<br />\n兩年後同白衫狗結婚"},{"pid":"840d6e4b841e267fd926a9d6170daef6130ed161","tid":1973291,"uid":201927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51996307fbff11bb2c6fbd266b63b093eba0a99a","tid":1973291,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:29:29.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26538ad78a77147f218900924322c5325f1af88e","tid":1973291,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbeabe765effd2fd3834f3d42475545af146115","tid":1973291,"uid":199804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"840d6e4b841e267fd926a9d6170daef6130ed161","tid":1973291,"uid":201927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"樓主唔係小明<br />\n小明是一個象徵<br />\n也許有很多小明"},{"pid":"2d993469c2e6791b9c09587b332aa470c70e54f8","tid":1973291,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足唔係condom"},{"pid":"23dc216392e02f0a9f9e667bc949295045c89292","tid":1973291,"uid":324602,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedB